The task thus takes the form of a classical prediction problem, either as a numerical coverage value or binarized class label. In Section (ref), we propose several heuristics and methods that can be used to predict coverage for a given document. To study this novel problem, we require evaluation data. The following section thus deals with the generation of a large and diverse document coverage dataset.